<i>and he'll slip and fall.</i>

256
00:17:58,840 --> 00:17:59,920
LEMONGRASS YE MENG

257
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,000
WHERE ARE YOU?

258
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:04,640
<i>Where are you? At the hospital or at home?</i>

259
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,320
<i>Home.</i>

260
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,520
<i>The snow's beautiful.</i>

261
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:27,560
HOME. THE SNOW'S BEAUTIFUL.

262
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,880
Aren't you cold? Close the window.

263
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:34,360
You don't get it. This is romantic.
It's all about the vibe.

264
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,600
Oh, give me a break.

265
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:41,800
Li Jinyu's birthday is coming up.
What should I get him?

266
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,760
You don't need to buy anything.
Just give him yourself.

267
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,480
So cheesy.
That's all you ever think about.

268
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:50,240
Hey, I'm allowed to think about it.

269
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,280
Your love power's not bad.
Why don't you teach me?

270
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,880
Just take it. It's yours.

271
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:00,840
I don't want yours. I want my own.

272
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,880
You don't get rituals.

273
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:04,120
Fine, fine, I don't get it.

274
00:19:04,200 --> 00:19:05,800
You city types come back here

275
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:08,920
and it's all about rituals and vibes.

276
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:09,960
Please, I'm begging you.

277
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,040
Okay, okay, I'll teach you.

278
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:12,480
But first, shut that window.

279
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:15,080
Why are you so obsessed with the window?

280
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,000
- It's freezing.
- Okay, okay, I get it.

281
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:18,240
Pick a color you like.

282
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:19,400
- Paint it however you want.
- Really?

283
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,560
Do one first. I'll see how good you are.

284
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:24,280
- Like this?
- Yeah, squeeze it like that.

285
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,760
Geez, that startled me.

286
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:28,680
Like that?

287
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:30,960
Yeah. Looks good!

288
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:32,320
Fang Ya'en.

289
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,480
You're not bad at this.

290
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:35,520
Later, whatever you make,
you're eating it yourself.

291
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:36,880
Here, let me show you.

292
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:56,160
<i>I booked your ticket.</i>

293
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,120
FLIGHT TICKET ISSUED

294
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:59,040
<i>Flight's tomorrow morning.</i>

295
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:00,640
<i>Driver will pick you up.</i>

296
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,040
YE MENG

297
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,600
WHERE ARE YOU? AT HOSPITAL OR AT HOME?

298
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,560
<i>I might</i>

299
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,600
<i>need to go to Jiangbei tomorrow.</i>

300
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:16,880
SEND

301
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:35,880
We gotta hurry.

302
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,800
If Li Jinyu finds out,
the surprise is ruined.

303
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,160
Seriously?

304
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,960
My leg's still not fully healed,

305
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,280
and you've got me
running around for a man?

306
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:45,480
Sorry, I forgot about your leg.
Here, give that to me.

307
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:47,440
Look at you.
Fireworks, cake, the whole package.

308
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:49,760
Aren't you worried
you're spoiling him rotten?

309
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,240
He's got a sharp memory
and an even sharper tongue.

310
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:54,160
I don't want him
throwing it back at me later

311
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:56,160
that the first birthday cake
I made him was hideous.

312
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,440
- Fine, fine.
- Give it here.

313
00:20:57,520 --> 00:20:58,600
No, it's fine.

314
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,640
No, hand it over.

315
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,960
I said it's fine.

316
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:02,240
You're impossible.

317
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,760
Careful.

318
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:06,400
327-3 XINGYI ROAD

319
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,640
OUTPATIENT

320
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:51,800
You two, wait outside.

321
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:52,960
Yes, Mrs. Li.

322
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:04,040
You've changed a lot.

323
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:07,080
Starting to look like a real man.

324
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,040
How's Grandma doing?

325
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:20,520
She fractured her leg a while back.

326
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:22,640
She's in rehab now,

327
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:24,360
but she's doing fine.

328
00:22:25,040 --> 00:22:26,120
Something that big,

329
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,080
and you didn't think to tell me?

330
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,160
I know

331
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:36,080
you still hold it against me.

332
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:38,880
All those years…

333
00:22:43,760 --> 00:22:45,120
I failed you.

334
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:47,520
And I failed your grandma.

335
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,080
How did you suddenly

336
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,840
get so sick?

337
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,800
Call it karma.

338
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:06,560
I've been in this hospital

339
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:08,360
over six months now.

340
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:11,760
I keep having nightmares.

341
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,240
I dream

342
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,960
<i>of that stormy night…</i>

343
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:21,480
<i>You clutching my hand…</i>

344
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,600
Mom!

345
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,080
<i>…crying, begging me…</i>

346
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,520
Mom!

347
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:27,560
- <i>…"Mom, don't send me away."</i>
- Mom!

348
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,200
Don't send me away!

349
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:42,760
Every time I wake up,

350
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:46,040
I feel like I should pick up the phone.

351
00:23:48,360 --> 00:23:50,160
On the way here, I read up on it.

352
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:53,160
First, you need a full exam,

353
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,720
then a bone marrow biopsy, right?

354
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:58,760
You'd really

355
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,440
donate your bone marrow to me?

356
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,040
Isn't that the reason

357
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,320
you reached out in the first place?

358
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,120
<i>The process</i>

359
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:10,480
<i>is complicated.</i>

360
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:13,000
<i>You'll have to stay here</i>

361
00:24:13,080 --> 00:24:14,360
<i>a few days.</i>

362
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,920
<i>I'll have someone</i>

363
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,960
<i>handle the admission paperwork.</i>

364
00:24:22,320 --> 00:24:25,560
QIAO MAIMAI

365
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,120
RESTART, POWER OFF

366
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,560
TAP TO POWER OFF

367
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:46,320
327-3 XINGYI ROAD

368
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:52,280
Maimai. You're home.

369
00:24:52,360 --> 00:24:53,640
Where's your cousin?

370
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:55,480
He's not here. I'm just feeding his dog.

371
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:57,400
Where did he go?

372
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:59,000
He went to Jiangbei.

373
00:24:59,080 --> 00:25:01,640
Jiangbei? That sudden?

374
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,200
Yeah, off to be a blood bank.

375
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:05,360
You mean donate blood?

376
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,600
No. Grandma said

377
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,280
his mom's really sick.

378
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:11,120
Nobody knows exactly what it is,

379
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,840
only that it's life-or-death.

380
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,080
She wanted him to donate marrow.

381
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:18,760
Now she's terrified of dying
and suddenly remembers she's got a son.

382
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,160
Only he would be that dumb.

383
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:23,080
The second he heard she was sick,
he dropped everything and went.

384
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:24,920
If you ask me,

385
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:27,040
he still hasn't let go of her.

386
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:30,760
And with his birthday coming up,

387
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:32,520
he's probably even hoping

388
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:34,600
she'll remember.

389
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:49,160
<i>I've heard donating marrow</i>
<i>hurts like hell.</i>

390
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:51,080
And he's over there all by himself,

391
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:53,800
with no one by his side
to ask if he's in pain.

392
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:56,120
It's just too pitiful.

393
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:08,160
LI JINYU

394
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,120
CALL

395
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:11,960
<i>Sorry,</i>

396
00:26:12,040 --> 00:26:14,640
<i>the subscriber you dialed is power off.</i>

397
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:50,120
ENTRANCE
EXIT

398
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,280
Jinyu, pull over.

399
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:24,960
Dad.

400
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,920
I need to ask you something.

401
00:27:30,360 --> 00:27:31,480
What is it?

402
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:38,040
Am I…

403
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:41,720
really not your son?

404
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:38,640
<i>Feng, you know you're Mommy's hero.</i>

405
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:42,680
My greatest hero.

406
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:44,080
I know you.

407
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:46,160
You can fight through this.

408
00:28:47,560 --> 00:28:48,760
<i>I believe in you.</i>

409
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:51,440
<i>You're such a strong boy.</i>

410
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,200
<i>Mommy's right here with you.</i>

411
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,400
<i>Don't be scared.</i>

412
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:25,760
OUTPATIENT

413
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:30,080
‪JIANGBEI DEYA HOSPITAL

414
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:31,400
BEDS 6B23-43
BEDS 6B01-22

415
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,720
Hi. I'm looking for a patient
named Li Jinyu.

416
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:35,920
Which room is he in?

417
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,880
One moment. I'll check.

418
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,760
B39. That way.

419
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:44,040
Thank you.

420
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:51,840
BEDS B38-39

421
00:30:35,840 --> 00:30:36,960
What?

422
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:47,720
It hurts…

423
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,160
Hurts a lot?

424
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,480
21:41 TUESDAY

425
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:41,680
YE MENG
MISSED CALLS

426
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:44,200
SIXTH FLOOR

427
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:52,400
Hello?

428
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:54,360
<i>Sorry…</i>

429
00:32:55,120 --> 00:32:57,160
I didn't have my phone with me.

430
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,320
I missed your calls.

431
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,040
Maimai told me everything.

432
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:04,040
Are you calling

433
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:05,920
to ask me to go to Jiangbei for you?

434
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,400
<i>Of course not.</i>

435
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,520
I'm calling because I dreamed about you.

436
00:33:09,600 --> 00:33:12,000
<i>I wanted to ask if you like</i>

437
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:13,320
<i>tofu cake.</i>

438
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,240
Back when I was in Jiangbei,

439
00:33:15,320 --> 00:33:17,160
there's this little shop.

440
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,560
We used to go there a lot.
The cake was amazing.

441
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:21,160
<i>If you want some,</i>

442
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,520
<i>I could bring it back.</i>

443
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:24,440
Forget it. Let's go together sometime.

444
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:26,960
Don't bother.

445
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:28,840
DIET KITCHEN

446
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,920
<i>Since I'm here in Jiangbei,</i>

447
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:34,000
<i>everyone wants to see me.</i>

448
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:36,200
Even if you came,

449
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,920
I wouldn't have time.

450
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:40,800
So, no meet-ups?

451
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,160
No meet-ups.

452
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,560
Fine.

453
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:30,080
Yu Ziyang!

454
00:34:30,159 --> 00:34:31,080
Mom!

455
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:34,719
Yu Ziyang!

456
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,480
I missed you so much.

457
00:34:36,560 --> 00:34:38,000
My sweet boy,

458
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:40,480
let me take a good look at you.
You've lost weight.

459
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:44,960
Leaving so soon?

460
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:49,280
You went through all that trouble
for such a performance.

461
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:52,000
You didn't have to.

462
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:54,360
I know. It's Li Zhuofeng who's sick.

463
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,480
You're sharp.

464
00:34:57,560 --> 00:35:00,160
I practiced in front of the mirror
for days to make it convincing.

465
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:03,760
I won't let you leave empty-handed.

466
00:35:04,720 --> 00:35:06,160
Take this. Call it compensation.

467
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,600
This is what I owe my dad.

468
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,480
The bone marrow…

469
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:14,000
Use it on whoever you want.

470
00:35:14,680 --> 00:35:15,960
I don't care to know.

471
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:19,200
Fine.

472
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,240
Have it your way.

473
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,000
Come on. Let's go home.

474
00:35:55,520 --> 00:35:57,360
I made you spicy chicken

475
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,280
and braised pork.

476
00:35:58,360 --> 00:35:59,920
- And more?
- Of course.

477
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:02,200
Everything you love.

478
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,320
Now hurry up.

479
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,360
Okay!

480
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,320
What are you doing at the station?

481
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,320
Someone sneaks off to Jiangbei

482
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:41,520
without a word,

483
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:43,080
and I can't block his way back?

484
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,520
My fault.

485
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,480
Here, tofu cake for you.

486
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:56,480
How did things go in Jiangbei? All sorted?

487
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,640
More or less.

488
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,680
It's over.

489
00:37:04,120 --> 00:37:05,960
That trip

490
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:08,000
drained you enough.

491
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:10,440
Any more and you'd collapse.

492
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,320
EXIT

493
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:33,120
Got your seatbelt on?

494
00:37:34,120 --> 00:37:35,320
Okay, let's go.

495
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:58,080
Got plans later?

496
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,480
Nothing important.

497
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:02,800
Then come to my place.

498
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,720
Mr. Li, after you.

499
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,640
Ready?

500
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,080
Happy Birthday!

501
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:44,440
I was planning to throw you
a grand ceremony.

502
00:38:44,520 --> 00:38:46,680
but you ran off to Jiangbei,

503
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,360
so this is all that's left.

504
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:50,280
But I baked this myself.

505
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,640
My first cake ever.

506
00:38:51,720 --> 00:38:54,000
And since you bought me tofu cake,

507
00:38:54,080 --> 00:38:56,360
I guess we can call it a mutual love.

508
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:59,960
Grand ceremony and mutual love.

509
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:01,280
That's not how those words are used.

510
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:04,680
I'll use them however I want.
I'll be right back.

511
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:16,120
Li Jinyu, look!

512
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:20,000
This is my gift for you.

513
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:24,880
Out of nowhere, you're giving me goldfish?

514
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:28,040
So your little black fish
won't be all alone.

515
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:29,560
You'll have a role model now.

516
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:33,120
No more loneliness,

517
00:39:33,200 --> 00:39:34,800
just some lively company.

518
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:41,960
And the next step…

519
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:45,520
Come on.

520
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:51,080
Make a wish first.

521
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:58,200
Li Jinyu! You'll need
to make a wish before you…

522
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:29,040
Not before you make your wish.

523
00:40:58,600 --> 00:41:00,360
Try the cake.

524
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,680
It's my first time baking,

525
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,600
but I think it actually turned out okay.

526
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,960
THANK YOU FOR FLYING WITH US
FROM NINGSUI TO JIANGBEI

527
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:11,200
- Have a bite.
- Were you in Jiangbei?

528
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:18,320
Your cousin was worried
something might happen to you.

529
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,440
So, I went in her place.

530
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:22,600
Then why didn't you tell me?

531
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:26,840
What do you mean? I told you on the phone.

532
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,120
But you didn't want to meet up.

533
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:31,440
So you just left like that.

534
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:38,480
I went to Jiangbei alone,
but someone wouldn't even see me.

535
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:41,040
My heart was already in pieces.
How could I stay?

536
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,600
What's wrong?

537
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,440
Do you still want to give us a try?

538
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:01,280
Ye Meng.

539
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:06,680
Do you still want to be with me?

