00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,480
Forget it.

541
00:42:15,600 --> 00:42:17,000
Pretend I didn't say anything.

542
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:23,760
Let me…

543
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:26,480
Let me ask you.

544
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:29,560
Are you asking me this

545
00:42:31,200 --> 00:42:32,880
because you actually love me,

546
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:35,800
or just because you're touched right now?

547
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:41,880
Because I want to be with someone
who truly loves me.

548
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:44,360
So, I'm not in a rush for an answer.

549
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:45,640
Take your time.

550
00:42:47,040 --> 00:42:47,920
Eat your cake.

551
00:42:49,160 --> 00:42:50,600
Go on. Taste it.

552
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:53,560
Though, I can't promise it isn't poisoned.

553
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:58,120
Look at that smiley face.
